      <title>联邦法官将联邦快递承包商的敲诈勒索索赔提交仲裁</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/federal-judge-sends-fedex-contractors-racketeering-claim-arbitration-2024-05-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名联邦法官周一裁定，一家在加州和俄勒冈州边境为联邦快递运送包裹的小企业必须就联邦快递针对该公司的敲诈勒索和其他涉嫌违法行为提出的索赔进行仲裁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/legal/federal-judge-sends-fedex-contractors-racketeering-claim-arbitration-2024-05-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 00:35:59 GMT</pubDate>
